<h3><strong></strong>&nbsp;<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/follow?original_referer=https%3A%2F%2Fabout.twitter.com%2Fresources%2Fbuttons%23follow&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;screen_name=SalmonArmORL&amp;tw_p=followbutton&amp;xd_token=8d9ba8a90f3f28"><img src="https://g.twimg.com/about/feature-corporate/image/followbutton.png" alt="" width="107" height="33" /></a></h3>
<p>The library has two book return&nbsp;bins - one open 24 hours&nbsp;behind the library, next to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Canadian Tire&nbsp;loading dock, and one inside the mall next to the library entrance and open during mall hours. Book drops are locked during extended closures (Easter and Christmas).</p>
<p>Please find our events below on the branch calendar, or search the <a href="news-events/event-search">ORL Calendar of Events</a>.&nbsp;</p></div>
    <div id="tab2" class="tab_content"><table id="openhours"><tr><td>Monday: </td><td>10:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.</td></tr><tr><td>Tuesday: </td><td>10:00 a.m. to 8:00 p.m.</td></tr><tr><td>Wednesday: </td><td>10:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.</td></tr><tr><td>Thursday: </td><td>10:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.</td></tr><tr><td>Friday: </td><td>10:00 a.m. to 8:00 p.m.</td></tr><tr><td>Saturday: </td><td>10:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.</td></tr><tr><td>Sunday: </td><td>Closed</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>All ORL branches are closed on statutory holidays</td></tr></table></div>
    <div id="tab3" class="tab_content"><p>Free parking is available in the mall parking lot.</p></div>
