<h3>Pyjama Story Time<span class="date">September 30, 2016</span></h3>
<p>Next Stop, DREAMLAND!
Grab a stuffie, get in your pj's and come down to the library for 30 minutes of fun bedtime stories and songs.
This program is geared toward ages 3-6, but all ages are welcome.
Dates:
Friday,...</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="branches/salmon-arm?event_id=3632">&raquo; Read More</a></p></div>
</div>
